            "question": {
              "S": "What is IAM?"
            },
            "answer": {
              "S": "Identity and Access Management (IAM) is a security framework that helps organizations manage and secure digital identities. IAM systems control who has access to what resources, and when. They also help to ensure that only authorized users can access sensitive data."
            }
